New Records: Rohit Sharma became the first man to five T20I hundreds
Key Match Events: Rohit Sharma took India from 22 for 4 to 212 for 4 through their highest partnership in T20Is
Rohit Sharma hit two sixes in the first Super Over
Rohit Sharma hit a six in the second Super Over
Nabi and Gurbaz ran overthrows off the body on the last ball of the first Super Over
Rohit Sharma was allowed to bat again in the second Super Over
Avesh Khan and Ravi Bishnoi bowled one ball each in the second Super Over
Nabi and Gurbaz could not impart enough power in their attempts to hit sixes
Gulbadin Naib's unbeaten 55 took the contest to Super Over
Karim Janat got out immediately after the 17th over
Naib found pace on the ball and nearly ran away with the match with some sensational hits
